footer.description: Ekibiina kya Gnosis Deutschland si kya kufuna magoba, kiri kimu ku bibiina bya Gnosis International, ky’ekolera ku kunoonyereza ku Gnostic okwalekebwawo V.M. Samael Aun Weor mu kitundu eky’okubiri eky’ekyasa eky’amakumi abiri.

i18n.untranslatedContent: Ebiri mu kino tebinakyusibwa mu lulimi lwo.

messages.automaticMessage: Essuula eno ekyusiddwa mu ngeri ya kompyuta okuva mu Lusipanya. Tennakeberwa muntu. Bw'oba oyagala okuyamba mu kukeberamu, tuukirira ffe nga onyiga wano.
messages.originalMessage: Ebiri mu ssuula eno byesigamye ku bigambo eby'omu Lusipanya ebyasooka.
messages.revisedMessage: Essuula eno ekebereddwa muntu era n'ekyusibwa okuva mu bigambo eby'omu Lusipanya ebyasooka. Bwe kiba kikyetaaga okulongoosebwa, tuukirira ffe nga onyiga wano.

page.draft: Bino bikyali mu nteekateeka era tebijja kuteekebwa mu nkola enkulu.
